Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Specialty Finance
Sub-Industry: Other Financial Services
Western Group Housing, LP operates as a special purpose entity. The Company was formed for the purpose of issuing debt securities to repay existing credit facilities, refinance indebtedness, and for acquisition purposes.




